18-year-old Emma Raducanu celebrates reaching the US Open tennis final at Flushing Meadows, New York. 

Raducanu, who is making her debut in the tournament, is the first British woman in a major singles final in 44 years. She faces off against Canadian teenager Leylah Fernandez in the final tomorrow. 

#tennis #sport #competition #usopen #newyork 

Danielle Parhizkaran-USA TODAY Sports

#transport #travel #sustainability #innovation #technology 

REUTERS/Michaela Rehle
